{"tid":2501594,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【！召集英語旁聽師！】","createTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T13:16:19.000Z","uid":94771,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4017fa12c9477161d970ec5bc0b98295b9b74b2b","tid":2501594,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZVuJDUYd9H3nCJ4W9wW9t7v4AF5HGjCinHuybMh44NCi?filename=Y0G9vzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0G9vzv.jpg&h=38a3624f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>【！召集英語旁聽師！】</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n英語審訊法庭要人！<br />\n越嚟越多社運案件進入審訊程序，<br />\n現有旁聽師可能要跑幾場，<br />\n面對英語審訊或者會感到無能為力，<br />\n如果自問英語能力唔錯，<br />\n但係又未搵到崗位嘅你，<br />\n怕羞唔知點踏出第一步嘅妳，<br />\n唔好左度右度，立即行動！<br />\n面對困難，請各位迎難而上！<br />\n等你！<br />\n<br />\nWe want YOU to sit in on English trials!<br />\nAs more antiELAB cases are entering trial proceedings, many sit in experts(旁聽師) sit in on several courts every day and find themselves incapable of understanding English trials.<br />\nIf you&rsquo;re looking for a way to contribute, and you happen to be fluent in English, your time has come! <br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t be shy and hesitant! Take the initiative to become an expert of sitting in on English trials. <br />\n<br />\nJoin us! <br />\n&middot;<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/tswconnection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftswconnection&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=5401de24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tswconnection</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT4jLVxGgb69WbQEFCHzMLwNvyr9mKZmrZiVsh57yTW2W?filename=2j11578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2j11578.jpg&h=df60caa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【五一勞動節聯合工會活動：四月工會街站】<br />\n<br />\n議會被廢，手足陷獄，但不代表民間就此就要消音。在今年的五一勞動節，我們對申請遊行成功再無幻想。然而，這並不代表我們放棄發聲。眾工會將在四月將會就不同議題設街站，到各區宣傳，揭露各種政府黑幕和政策問題，讓香港人看見，這一群留低的香港人，可以做到的事。<br />\n<br />\n香港的公民社會必須站在第一線，去抗衡「新秩序」的形成。工會在每個行業的身位中，「守住條線」，連結更廣泛的公民社會，是工會戰線肩負的歷史任務。<br />\n<br />\n工會亦會於街站向港人派發「揸宗旨抗暴政」卡，呼籲香港人五一以行動展示對抗決心，一息尚存，抗爭到底。"},{"pid":"4ddc314a99781f34743640797a79b444d1d6c731","tid":2501594,"uid":154490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"560c600462f63e4c6900280ae525bca8256ed385","tid":2501594,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"221efe265de14160166e679aecaa50e72c6e0283","tid":2501594,"uid":154490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fbd5e5171e5f094a0ad5ed74c51ac498b1246d","tid":2501594,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"64f11568c82456a44a2324bfdec51d16c592589c","tid":2501594,"uid":154490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c8e47ae2ad65163468c4c7c4728eb0f86cebf6","tid":2501594,"uid":142002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"旁聽師要點做？<br />\n想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/plea